Following her recruitment as CEO, Duncan stated "I am completely honored and super excited to have the opportunity to lead Victoria’s peak youth music organization into its next chapter.

After 30 years of incorporation, it is time for The Push to redefine our positioning as a relevant and dynamic organization in fostering Victoria’s future generations of music industry leaders and audiences."
